src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/producer/internals/RecordAccumulatorTest.java**\n   - Comprehensive test suite for RecordAccumulator\n   - Uses: RecordAccumulator, RecordAccumulator.ReadyCheckResult, RecordAccumulator.AppendCallbacks, RecordAccumulator.PartitionerConfig\n\n7. **clients/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/producer/KafkaProducerTest.java**\n   - Uses: RecordAccumulator.AppendCallbacks, RecordAccumulator.RecordAppendResult\n   - Mocks RecordAccumulator for testing KafkaProducer\n\n8. **clients/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/producer/internals/SenderTest.java**\n   - Field: `private RecordAccumulator accumulator`\n   - Uses: RecordAccumulator, RecordAccumulator.AppendCallbacks, RecordAccumulator.PartitionerConfig\n\n9. **clients/src/test/java/org/apache/kafka/clients/producer/internals/TransactionManagerTest.java**\n   - Field: `private RecordAccumulator accumulator`\n   - Creates and uses RecordAccumulator instances for testing\n\n### Benchmark Files\n\n10. **jmh-benchmarks/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/jmh/producer/RecordAccumulatorFlushBenchmark.java**\n    - Import: `org.apache.kafka.clients.producer.internals.RecordAccumulator`\n    - Field: `private RecordAccumulator accum`\n    - Usage: Creates RecordAccumulator instances for JMH performance benchmarking\n\n### Inner Classes Summary\nThe following inner classes/interfaces within RecordAccumulator will also need rename references updated:\n- **RecordAppendResult**: Used in KafkaProducer and KafkaProducerTest\n- **ReadyCheckResult**: Used in Sender and RecordAccumulatorTest\n- **AppendCallbacks**: Interface used in KafkaProducer, KafkaProducerTest, SenderTest, and RecordAccumulatorTest\n- **PartitionerConfig**: Used in KafkaProducer, SenderTest, and RecordAccumulatorTest\n\nTotal files affected: 11 (1 main definition + 4 supporting main sources + 5 test files + 1 benchmark file)"
